==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Demersion
<hw>De*mer"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>demersio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of plunging into a
fluid; a drowning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being overwhelmed in water, or as if in
water.</def> <rj><au>Ray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Demesmerize</ent>⟦br⟧
